BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Human Mind Youth Creates 2026
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260724T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260724T203000
DTSTAMP:20260721T085036Z
UID:occ-4121@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:An original devised play about artificial intelligence\, creat
 ed and performed by the Youth Creates 2026 Ensemble.\n\nHuman Mind is an o
 riginal play about artificial intelligence and its impact\, devised by the
  Youth Creates 2026 Ensemble. Each summer\, 7 Stages' young performers wor
 k with teaching artists to build a production from scratch\, drawing on th
 eir workshops and their own experience of the world\; this performance is 
 the result. Tickets use a tiered pricing structure\, with a 'Pay it Forwar
 d' option that subsidizes lower-cost seats.
GEO:33.7639125;-84.3509364
LAST-MODIFIED:20260721T084831Z
LOCATION:7 Stages Theatre\, 1105 Euclid Ave NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
